{
  "title": "ISic000152. Funerary inscription for a Claud[---] Fort[---]",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Tuuli Ahlholm, Alex Antoniou</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Claud\n                    Fortu\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Claud\">Claud[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Fortu\">Fortụ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"vixit\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">vix(it)</span>  <span data-text=\"annis\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">[an(nis)</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Tuuli Ahlholm, Alex Antoniou</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Claud\n                    Fortu\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Claud\">CLAUD[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Fortu\">FORT.[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"vixit\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">VIX</span><span data-text=\"annis\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">[...</span><span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic000152_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-04.\" src=\"ISic000152_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000152.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-04.\" src=\"ISic000152-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic000152_rear_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-04.\" src=\"ISic000152_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000152_rear.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-04.\" src=\"ISic000152_rear-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text after autopsy</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0001-7077-0703\">Alex Antoniou</a></p>  <p>Claud[...] Fortu[...] lived for [...]</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The lack of a praenomen on the stone means that it is most likely that the epitaph was for a woman, most plausibly called Claudia Fortunata, but as Bivona observes there are instances of male individuals lacking a praenomen in the Termini corpus also (e.g. <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000056\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000153</a>), so this is hardly conclusive.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> VIII 703 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002649\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002649</a>  </li><li> Fiorelli NSA 1889 139 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392</a>  </li><li> Bivona 1994 71 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>The text is irregularly and shakily carved. Letter height and width differ even on the same line, and the T on line 2 is significantly taller than other letters. Simple serifs used. The vertical bar for the 'R' in line 2 is bisected by a long horizontal foot. At the end of line 2, the top of a serifed downstroke is just visible after the T.</p> Line 1  63-69  Line 2  49-50  Line 3  34  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
  "divs": [
    {
