      "html": "<div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Tuuli Ahlholm, Alex Antoniou</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Claud\n                    Fortu\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Claud\">Claud[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Fortu\">Fortụ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"vixit\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">vix(it)</span>  <span data-text=\"annis\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">[an(nis)</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Tuuli Ahlholm, Alex Antoniou</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Claud\n                    Fortu\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Claud\">CLAUD[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Fortu\">FORT.[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"vixit\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">VIX</span><span data-text=\"annis\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">[...</span><span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div>"
